dc_title_s: Hydrography, Edge Features: Montgomery County, Maryland, 2015
dc_description_s: This is a feature class in the geodatabase Planimetric Mapping Features: Montgomery County, Maryland, 2015. The data set contains hydrographic features as identified from the development of planimetric mapping from aerial photography as part of the GeoMaP initiative. It contains attribute which identify the specific features as well as a GeoMaP feature code assignment.
dc_creator_sm: Montgomery County Planning Department of the Maryland National Capital Park and Planning Commission
dc_publisher_sm: The Maryland-National Capital Park and Planning Commission
